(this name uses spanish naming customs: the first or paternal family name is merhi and the second or maternal family name is muntan.) roberto merhi muntan (born 22 march 1991) is a spanish racing driver who, in 2015, drove in formula one for the manor marussia f1 team as well as the formula renault 3.5 series for pons racing. merhi is also a part of the revitalized mercedes-benz junior team, together with christian vietoris and robert wickens. in 2011, merhi won the formula 3 euro series championship, while driving for prema powerteam.